<h2>9. Data Deletion</h2>
<p>
  You have the right to request the deletion of your personal data at any time. 
  To do so, please contact us at <a href="mailto:info@ozonehotel.net">info@ozonehotel.net</a> with your request.
  Upon verifying your identity, we will process your request within a reasonable timeframe, typically within 30 days.
</p>
<p>
  Please note that we may retain certain data where required by law, for security, or for legitimate business purposes (e.g., accounting records, fraud prevention).
</p>
